الظواهر،"},{"startTime":"+00000000.00:00:32.048000000","endTime":"+00000000.00:00:35.757000000","text":"إلا أننا لم نشهد من قبل شيئًا كهذا."}],"de":[{"startTime":"+00000000.00:00:00.833000000","endTime":"+00000000.00:00:03.833000000","text":"Plötzlich ... kam der Rest von ihnen."},{"startTime":"+00000000.00:00:28.331000000","endTime":"+00000000.00:00:32.690000000","text":"NACHRICHTENSPRECHERIN: Seltsame Phänomene sind auf der Insel zwar alles andere als ungewöhnlich,"},{"startTime":"+00000000.00:00:32.748000000","endTime":"+00000000.00:00:36.657000000","text":"doch so etwas haben wir bisher noch nie erlebt."}],"en":[{"startTime":"+00000000.00:00:00.833000000","endTime":"+00000000.00:00:03.833000000","text":"Then.. the rest of them showed up."},{"startTime":"+00000000.00:00:28.331000000","endTime":"+00000000.00:00:31.790000000","text":"NEWSCASTER:  While the island is certainly no stranger to strange phenomena, "},{"startTime":"+00000000.00:00:32.048000000","endTime":"+00000000.00:00:35.757000000","text":"never before have we seen anything quite like this."}],"es":[{"startTime":"+00000000.00:00:00.833000000","endTime":"+00000000.00:00:03.833000000","text":"Entonces... aparecieron los demás."},{"startTime":"+00000000.00:00:28.331000000","endTime":"+00000000.00:00:31.990000000","text":"LOCUTORA: Si bien no es extraño que en la isla se den fenómenos extraños,"},{"startTime":"+00000000.00:00:32.048000000","endTime":"+00000000.00:00:35.757000000","text":"nunca habíamos visto nada parecido a esto."}],"es-419":[{"startTime":"+00000000.00:00:00.833000000","endTime":"+00000000.00:00:03.833000000","text":"Entonces..., aparecieron los demás."},{"startTime":"+00000000.00:00:28.331000000","endTime":"+00000000.00:00:31.790000000","text":"PERIODISTA:  Aunque no es raro que en la isla haya fenómenos extraños, "},{"startTime":"+00000000.00:00:32.048000000","endTime":"+00000000.00:00:35.757000000","text":"nunca habíamos visto algo como esto antes."}],"fr":[{"startTime":"+00000000.00:00:00.833000000","endTime":"+00000000.00:00:03.833000000","text":"Et là, tous les autres sont apparus."},{"startTime":"+00000000.00:00:28.331000000","endTime":"+00000000.00:00:31.790000000","text":"PRÉSENTATRICE : Si l'île a connu bon nombre de phénomènes inhabituels,"},{"startTime":"+00000000.00:00:32.048000000","endTime":"+00000000.00:00:35.757000000","text":"celui-ci semble d'ores et déjà défrayer la chronique."}],"it":[{"startTime":"+00000000.00:00:00.833000000","endTime":"+00000000.00:00:03.833000000","text":"Poi... sono arrivati gli altri."},{"startTime":"+00000000.00:00:28.331000000","endTime":"+00000000.00:00:31.790000000","text":"GIORNALISTA TG: L'isola non è certo nuova a vari fenomeni bizzarri,"},{"startTime":"+00000000.00:00:32.026000000","endTime":"+00000000.00:00:35.674000000","text":"tuttavia non abbiamo mai assistito a nulla di questo genere."}],"ja":[{"startTime":"+00000000.00:00:00.833000000","endTime":"+00000000.00:00:03.833000000","text":"そして… 他のやつらも現れたんだ"},{"startTime":"+00000000.00:00:28.331000000","endTime":"+00000000.00:00:31.790000000","text":"ニュースキャスター:  この島では奇妙な現象が日常茶飯事ですが―― "},{"startTime":"+00000000.00:00:32.048000000","endTime":"+00000000.00:00:35.757000000","text":"これほどまでの事態は未だかつてなかったものです"}],"ko":[{"startTime":"+00000000.00:00:00.833000000","endTime":"+00000000.00:00:03.833000000","text":"그리고… 나머지가 나타났어요"},{"startTime":"+00000000.00:00:28.331000000","endTime":"+00000000.00:00:31.790000000","text":"아나운서:  여태까지 섬에 기이한 현상들이 많이 일어나긴 했지만"},{"startTime":"+00000000.00:00:32.048000000","endTime":"+00000000.00:00:35.757000000","text":"지금 같은 상황은 저희도 처음 보는 상황입니다
"}],"pl":[{"startTime":"+00000000.00:00:00.833000000","endTime":"+00000000.00:00:03.833000000","text":"Nagle ... pojawiła się reszta."},{"startTime":"+00000000.00:00:28.331000000","endTime":"+00000000.00:00:31.790000000","text":"PREZENTER: Choć dziwne zjawiska nie są na wyspie żadną nowością,"},{"startTime":"+00000000.00:00:32.048000000","endTime":"+00000000.00:00:35.757000000","text":"to jeszcze nigdy wcześniej nie widzieliśmy czegoś takiego."}],"pt-br":[{"startTime":"+00000000.00:00:00.833000000","endTime":"+00000000.00:00:03.833000000","text":"Depois... o restante apareceu."},{"startTime":"+00000000.00:00:28.331000000","endTime":"+00000000.00:00:32.452000000","text":"APRESENTADORA: Embora a Ilha já tenha sido palco de diversos fenômenos estranhos,"},{"startTime":"+00000000.00:00:32.681000000","endTime":"+00000000.00:00:35.554000000","text":"nunca vimos nada desse tipo antes."}],"ru":[{"startTime":"+00000000.00:00:00.833000000","endTime":"+00000000.00:00:03.833000000","text":"Вдруг... появились другие."},{"startTime":"+00000000.00:00:28.331000000","endTime":"+00000000.00:00:31.790000000","text":"РЕПОРТЁР:  Что ж, на острове нередко происходят загадочные события, "},{"startTime":"+00000000.00:00:32.048000000","endTime":"+00000000.00:00:35.757000000","text":"но такого мы ещё никогда не наблюдали."}],"tr":[{"startTime":"+00000000.00:00:00.898000000","endTime":"+00000000.00:00:03.789000000","text":"Sonra... aniden diğerleri çıkageldi."},{"startTime":"+00000000.00:00:28.334000000","endTime":"+00000000.00:00:31.718000000","text":"MUHABİR: Adada garip olaylara
artık alışmış olsak bile..."},{"startTime":"+00000000.00:00:31.976000000","endTime":"+00000000.00:00:35.757000000","text":"...daha önce böyle bir şeyle
hiçbirimiz karşılaşmadık."},{"startTime":"+00000000.00:01:09.465000000","endTime":"+00000000.00:01:13.796000000","text":"FORTNITE - 7. SEZON:
İSTİLA"}],"zh-CN":[{"startTime":"+00000000.00:00:00.833000000","endTime":"+00000000.00:00:03.833000000","text":"突然之间，其余的人也来了。"},{"startTime":"+00000000.00:00:28.331000000","endTime":"+00000000.00:00:31.790000000","text":"新闻播音员：虽说岛上奇特之事屡见不鲜，"},{"startTime":"+00000000.00:00:32.048000000","endTime":"+00000000.00:00:35.757000000","text":"但这样的状况还是前所未有。"}]}
